{"thag15.2:0.1":"Theragatha 15.2 ","thag15.2:0.2":"Solasakanipata ","thag15.2:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag15.2:0.4":"Udayittheragatha ","thag15.2:1.1":"“Manussabhutam sambuddham, ","thag15.2:1.2":"Attadantam samahitam; ","thag15.2:1.3":"Iriyamanam brahmapathe, ","thag15.2:1.4":"Cittassupasame ratam. ","thag15.2:2.1":"Yam manussa namassanti, ","thag15.2:2.2":"sabbadhammana paragum; ","thag15.2:2.3":"Devapi tam namassanti, ","thag15.2:2.4":"iti me arahato sutam. ","thag15.2:3.1":"Sabbasamyojanatitam, ","thag15.2:3.2":"vana nibbanamagatam; ","thag15.2:3.3":"Kamehi nekkhammaratam, ","thag15.2:3.4":"muttam selava kancanam. ","thag15.2:4.1":"Sa ve accaruci nago, ","thag15.2:4.2":"himavavanne siluccaye; ","thag15.2:4.3":"Sabbesam naganamanam, ","thag15.2:4.4":"saccanamo anuttaro. ","thag15.2:5.1":"Nagam vo kittayissami, ","thag15.2:5.2":"na hi agum karoti so; ","thag15.2:5.3":"Soraccam avihimsa ca, ","thag15.2:5.4":"pada nagassa te duve. ","thag15.2:6.1":"Sati ca sampajannanca, ","thag15.2:6.2":"carana nagassa tepare; ","thag15.2:6.3":"Saddhahattho mahanago, ","thag15.2:6.4":"upekkhasetadantava. ","thag15.2:7.1":"Sati giva siro panna, ","thag15.2:7.2":"vimamsa dhammacintana; ","thag15.2:7.3":"Dhammakucchisamavaso, ","thag15.2:7.4":"viveko tassa valadhi. ","thag15.2:8.1":"So jhayi assasarato, ","thag15.2:8.2":"ajjhattam susamahito; ","thag15.2:8.3":"Gaccham samahito nago, ","thag15.2:8.4":"thito nago samahito. ","thag15.2:9.1":"Sayam samahito nago, ","thag15.2:9.2":"nisinnopi samahito; ","thag15.2:9.3":"Sabbattha samvuto nago, ","thag15.2:9.4":"esa nagassa sampada. ","thag15.2:10.1":"Bhunjati anavajjani, ","thag15.2:10.2":"savajjani na bhunjati; ","thag15.2:10.3":"Ghasamacchadanam laddha, ","thag15.2:10.4":"sannidhim parivajjayam. ","thag15.2:11.1":"Samyojanam anum thulam, ","thag15.2:11.2":"sabbam chetvana bandhanam; ","thag15.2:11.3":"Yena yeneva gacchati, ","thag15.2:11.4":"anapekkhova gacchati. ","thag15.2:12.1":"Yathapi udake jatam, ","thag15.2:12.2":"pundarikam pavaddhati; ","thag15.2:12.3":"Nopalippati toyena, ","thag15.2:12.4":"sucigandham manoramam. ","thag15.2:13.1":"Tatheva ca loke jato, ","thag15.2:13.2":"buddho loke viharati; ","thag15.2:13.3":"Nopalippati lokena, ","thag15.2:13.4":"toyena padumam yatha. ","thag15.2:14.1":"Mahagini pajjalito, ","thag15.2:14.2":"anaharopasammati; ","thag15.2:14.3":"Angaresu ca santesu, ","thag15.2:14.4":"nibbutoti pavuccati. ","thag15.2:15.1":"Atthassayam vinnapani, ","thag15.2:15.2":"upama vinnuhi desita; ","thag15.2:15.3":"Vinnissanti mahanaga, ","thag15.2:15.4":"nagam nagena desitam. ","thag15.2:16.1":"Vitarago vitadoso, ","thag15.2:16.2":"Vitamoho anasavo; ","thag15.2:16.3":"Sariram vijaham nago, ","thag15.2:16.4":"Parinibbissatyanasavo”ti. ","thag15.2:16.5":"… Udayi thero … ","thag15.2:16.6":"Solasakanipato nitthito. ","thag15.2:17.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag15.2:17.1":"Kondanno ca udayi ca, ","thag15.2:17.2":"thera dve te mahiddhika; ","thag15.2:17.3":"Solasamhi nipatamhi, ","thag15.2:17.4":"gathayo dve ca timsa cati. "}